\subsection{The Wilcoxon Signed-Rank Test}{

For each pair of measurements, the Wilcoxon signed-rank test:
\enumerate{
\item Computes differences between the two measurements
\item Ranks the absolute differences
\item Computes a Z-statistic based on the rank sums
\item Uses normal approximation with tie correction
}
